commentPostTextItems.html: Shahid Afridi put up a typically brutal show to get Pakistan into the game but it was too little and too late to hide the dismal performance of the top order. Once again, they collapsed in a heap and left the lower middle order with too much too do. South Africa were clinical and efficient.
Man of the Match: AB de Villiers.
That's it from me, Sriram Veera. Now .. to the Rugby final on Saturday. Alvida!
